tlajtoli tlen ax tlauel chikauak. “Nochipa tijmatiyayaj nopa.”
“Pero Dumbledore kiijtok eliyaya ipan to lado!” kiijtok Tonks.
“Nochipa nimoiljuiyaya Dumbledore monekiyaya kimatis se keski tlamantli tlen Snape
tlen ax tijchijque. . . .”
